data.description: Amazing 2021 Built home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths on half acre lot!. Formal living with windows for lots of light & dining room with tray ceiling. Neutral colors throughout! Move in Ready! Plenty of closets for storage and a walk-in attic storage! Electric fireplace in the family room, off of the eat in area & kitchen with slider to back patio & creative deck area perfect for entertaining! You will be amazed! All kitchen appliances included!
